
Loading data form the csv file

```{r}
filename <- "temp/android_dataset_6_4.csv"
dataset <- read.csv(filename, header=TRUE, sep=",", row.names="Project")
dataset$Project <- NULL
```

Load our neuralnet model
```{r}
neuralnet <- list()
neuralnet <- neuralnet_model(dataset)
neuralnet <- m_fit.neuralnet(neuralnet, dataset)
print(neuralnet)
```

Visualize neuralnet
```{r}
plot.nnet(neuralnet$m)
```

Predict result
```{r}
predictions <- m_predict.neuralnet(neuralnet, modelData)
print(predictions)
```
